nodes.text: Coral was a type of sea animal found on Pantolomin, Sedri, Rugosa, Dac, Drexel, Baralou, Naboo, and other worlds. The Mon Calamari built beautiful cities with towers and spires among the coral reefs of their home planet Dac. Coral was not just limited to aquatic life, however, an example being the land coral of Rugosa.
